# Install scriptlet generated by arch-repackage.
#
# Only PACKAGE-SPECIFIC actions belong here. Do NOT call systemctl
# daemon-reload, systemd-sysusers, systemd-tmpfiles or udevadm here: on a real
# Arch system those are run automatically by the pacman hooks shipped in the
# `systemd` package whenever a matching file is installed. Duplicating them is
# redundant and can mask ordering bugs.
#
# Leave a function body as `:` when there is nothing to do.

post_install() {
%POST_INSTALL%
}

post_upgrade() {
%POST_UPGRADE%
}

post_remove() {
%POST_REMOVE%
}
